    <section id="consumables">
        <h2>Consumables</h2>

        <h3>Flasks</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Phial of Tepid Versatility</strong> - Good balance between defensive and offensive boosts.</li>
            <li><strong>Phial of Static Empowerment</strong> - Great when you’re confident on bosses with little movement requirements.</li>
            <li><strong>Phial of Elemental Chaos</strong> - Risky but high reward in DPS heavy situations.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Food</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Feast Buffs</strong> - Use what your raid provides.</li>
            <li><strong>Individual Food</strong> - Examples: Timely Demise (Haste) or Grand Banquet of the Kalu'ak.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Potions</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Elemental Potion of Power</strong> - Best during burst phases.</li>
            <li><strong>Refreshing Healing Potion</strong> - Keep for emergencies.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Weapon Oils</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Buzzing Rune</strong> - Best for Haste uptime.</li>
            <li><strong>Howling Rune</strong> - Use if Haste is capped.</li>
            <li><strong>Chirping Rune</strong> - Defensive fallback.</li>
        </ul>

